Package co.cask.coopr.common.queue

Queues implemented on top of zookeeper.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
QueuedElement Represents an Element that is queued.
QueueGroup A group of TrackingQueues that usually serve a similar purpose.
TrackingQueue Queue that tracks consuming of the elements and may re-add elements that were attempted to be consumed.
 

Class Summary
Element The element to be placed in the TrackingQueue.
GroupElement An element taken from a QueueGroup, indicating which queue the element was taken from as well as the element itself.
QueueMetrics A snapshot of metrics related to a TrackingQueue.
 

Enum Summary
QueueType Types of Queues.
TrackingQueue.ConsumingStatus Defines Tracking Queue Consuming Status.
TrackingQueue.PossessionState Defines PossessionState.
 

Package co.cask.coopr.common.queue Description

Queues implemented on top of zookeeper.
